1: Download the latest Nyrion release of the releases page (https://github.com/Gayware64/Nyrion/releases/tag/v1.4)
2: Download the .py file and save it somewhere.
3: Download the latest Python release. (https://www.python.org/downloads/)
4: Install the EXE file of python
5: Install pip (https://packaging.python.org/en/latest/tutorials/installing-packages/)
6: Install Tkinter if you got v1.3 or higher (pip install tk) (CMD)
7: Double click the Nyrion PY file.
8: Enjoy Nyrion.

If there are any bugs please DM me on twitter. https://x.com/NyrionOfficial
